# Build directories
build/
modules/*/build/
**/build/

# CMake generated files
CMakeCache.txt
CMakeFiles/
cmake_install.cmake
Makefile
*.cmake

# Compiled files
*.so
*.o
*.a

# Qt generated files
*_autogen/
*.qmlc
*.jsc
moc_*
qrc_*

# IDE files
.vscode/
.idea/
*.user
*.swp
*.swo

# Installation directories (if you installed locally for testing)
.local/
```

## Recommended Repository Structure:
```
your-quickshell-config/
├── .gitignore
├── README.md
├── shell.qml
├── Colors.qml
├── WorkspaceOverview.qml
├── plugins/                    # ← Include this (source only)
│   └── HyprlandMonitor/
│       ├── README.md           # Build instructions
│       ├── CMakeLists.txt
│       ├── hyprlandmonitor.hpp
│       └── hyprlandmonitor.cpp
└── screenshots/                # Optional
